OL,3,C'Drugs, cockroaches and mice': HMP
OL,4,CPentonville branded 'appalling' in new
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FThree prisoners killed themselves at
OL,8,FPentonville prison this year alone,
OL,9,Faccording to a new report, which said
OL,10,Fconditions were "appalling" and rooms
OL,11,Finfested with cockroaches and mice.
OL,13,FThe Inspectorate of Prisons also found
OL,14,Fstaff asleep or absent when they
OL,15,Fshould have been supervising
OL,16,Fvulnerable men.
OL,18,FThe north London jail was placed into
OL,19,Fspecial measures earlier this year
OL,20,Fafter the extent of the inhumane
OL,21,Fliving standards were first exposed.
