OL,7,FInspectors found that 44 per cent of
OL,8,Fprisoners in the jail felt unsafe at
OL,9,Fthe time of the inspection - they said
OL,10,Fdrugs that were brought into the
OL,11,Fprison were driving up levels of
OL,12,Fviolence and the smell of cannabis
OL,13,Ffilled the air.
