OL,3,C'Drugs, cockroaches and mice': HMP
OL,4,CPentonville branded 'appalling' in new
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FNew arrivals at the prison received
OL,8,Fshockingly little support despite
OL,9,Foften high levels of risk and need;
OL,10,Fsome were locked in induction cells
OL,11,Fwithout bedding, pillows or cutlery,
OL,12,Fand others were scattered across the
OL,13,Fjail with staff unable to locate or
OL,14,Fidentify them.
