OL,3,C'Drugs, cockroaches and mice': HMP
OL,4,CPentonville branded 'appalling' in new
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FChief Inspector Charlie Taylor said:
OL,8,F"Pentonville is never an easy jail to
OL,9,Frun, with overcrowded cells, crumbling
OL,10,Finfrastructure and a fast-changing
OL,11,Fpopulation that includes many
OL,12,Fprisoners who are mentally ill,
OL,13,Faddicted to drugs and homeless, or who
OL,14,Fare involved with criminal gangs.
OL,16,F"However, we found comprehensive
OL,17,Ffailures by leaders to make sure that
OL,18,Fthere was effective oversight and
OL,19,Fmanagement of some of the basic
OL,20,Foperations of a reception prison.
