OL,3,C'Drugs, cockroaches and mice': HMP
OL,4,CPentonville branded 'appalling' in new
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,F"It will take support and investment
OL,8,Ffrom the prison service to turn round
OL,9,Fthis troubled jail."
OL,11,FPoor relationships between prisoners
OL,12,Fand staff were affecting the rest of
OL,13,Fthe population; there was a noticeable
OL,14,Flack of empathy and care, and 50 per
OL,15,Fcent reported that they had been
OL,16,Fbullied or victimised by staff, the
OL,17,Freport said.
OL,19,FThe report described the wings as
OL,20,F"dirty, noisy and chaotic".
