OL,3,C'Drugs, cockroaches and mice': HMP
OL,4,CPentonville branded 'appalling' in new
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,F"Most prisoners spent more than 22
OL,8,Fhours a day locked in poorly
OL,9,Fventilated, overcrowded cells, with
OL,10,Flittle chance of getting to work or
OL,11,Feducation," the report said.
OL,13,FThe prisoners did not attend their
OL,14,Factivities and were unprepared for
OL,15,Femployment - this meant there were low
OL,16,Fnumbers in work after their release.
