OL,3,C'Drugs, cockroaches and mice': HMP
OL,4,CPentonville branded 'appalling' in new
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FSome prisoners were also being held
OL,8,Funlawfully for extra days past their
OL,9,Fsentence because the prison had
OL,10,Fincorrectly calculated the release
OL,11,Fdays.
OL,13,FThe report did find some positives,
OL,14,Fincluding the health service and a
OL,15,Fsubstance-free living unit to help
OL,16,Ftackle addictions, and a programme to
OL,17,Fsupport younger men.
