OL,7,FA Ministry of Justice spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid: "This is a deeply concerning
OL,9,Freport that further underlines the
OL,10,Fprisons crisis inherited by this
OL,11,FGovernment.
OL,13,F"We are already taking urgent action
OL,14,Fat HMP Pentonville ` detailed in our
OL,15,Fcomprehensive action plan published in
OL,16,FAugust - including strengthening
OL,17,Fleadership, additional training for
OL,18,Fstaff and significant refurbishment of
OL,19,Fwings.
